originalText.text: I love leaving feedback where it is deserved. I'm not shy to say that Ebelyn has been my therapist for two years, and every time I come out of her office, she makes me do internal research, in such a positive way. She really has inspiring words, but helps you grow. It will be difficult to make a change to another therapist, when I have such an understanding with Ebelyn, and she is always willing to be there when I need her. She is fantastic. If you are seeking for someone that you want to feel like you are being listened to. Go to her!, pick her at the clinic. I hope to continue working with her, especially now. Sometimes, therapist and counselors are not given enough recognition, and she is an individual that really deserves the Kuddos!
